{"tid":1848023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"暫停自由行係冇用！中國人來香港，只需要中國護照加第三地機票就得！","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T09:39:39.000Z","uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79df50dddcb11d461ff97800214ae3800b3a3824","tid":1848023,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"中國外交部網站寫得清清楚楚：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cgct/chn/lszj/cpt_traveldoc/cpt_traveldoc_chn/t212535.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fce%2Fcgct%2Fchn%2Flszj%2Fcpt_traveldoc%2Fcpt_traveldoc_chn%2Ft212535.htm&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=9447f1c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/ce/cgct/chn/lszj/cpt_traveldoc/cpt_traveldoc_chn/t212535.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;持中华人民共和国护照，自海外途经香港前往第三国（或地区），凭有效护照和联程机票，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可免办进入许可并在香港停留7天</span></span>。目的地为中国内地或澳门者，可不出示联程机票。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHq5EdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHq5EdN.jpg&h=a892ac0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08cf4f4c255db1652f70388ed031a582ac31a32a","tid":1848023,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=86948f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=07c10d30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&h=f2bcfe36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/houseforeign/status/1221916701463400448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhouseforeign%2Fstatus%2F1221916701463400448&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=4481b94b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhouseforeign%2Fstatus%2F1221916701463400448&h=f70d74fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/houseforeign/status/1221916701463400448</a><br />\n3. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BarrySheerman/status/1222048272627458049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBarrySheerman%2Fstatus%2F1222048272627458049&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=efeec8cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBarrySheerman%2Fstatus%2F1222048272627458049&h=c9836eaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BarrySheerman/status/1222048272627458049</a><br />\n更加多 link 入 bot 搵， tasklist 二十四小時持續更新 <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n【twitter戰線】美國及英國議員要求英國政府禁用華為建5G<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846357</a>"},{"pid":"058e28557f4dd1e5973416df249c2a4d93bf39fc","tid":1848023,"uid":6741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa5d1cea74e1